text: Li Lixin (; born 15 February 1989) is a Chinese professional racing cyclist. She rides for China Chongming-Liv-Champion System Pro Cycling. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
